2026-05-15T23:27:22.0327646Z 254            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-15T23:27:22.0328031Z 255            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-15T23:27:22.0328375Z 256            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
